##### Functions #####
### Basic functions
DestroyFunc Move-or-Raise
AddToFunc Move-or-Raise 
+ I Raise
+ M Move

DestroyFunc Move-or-Iconify
AddToFunc Move-or-Iconify 
+ I Raise
+ M Move
+ D Iconify

DestroyFunc Resize-or-Raise
AddToFunc Resize-or-Raise 
+ I Raise
+ M Resize

### Builtin overrides
DestroyFunc WindowListFunc
AddToFunc WindowListFunc
+ I Iconify off
+ I FlipFocus
+ I Raise
+ I WarpToWindow 50 50

### Config change functions
DestroyFunc ToggleEdgeScroll
AddToFunc ToggleEdgeScroll
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.edge_scroll on) EdgeScroll 0 0
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.edge_scroll on) Exec xmessage -center \
	"Paging is now disabled." -title Info
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.edge_scroll on) Exec \
	$FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 2 "0 0" "100 100" "off" "on"
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.edge_scroll on) InfoStoreAdd edge_scroll off
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I EdgeScroll 100 100
+ I Exec xmessage -center "Paging is now enabled." -title Info
+ I Exec $FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 2 "100 100" "0 0" "on" "off"
+ I InfoStoreAdd edge_scroll on

DestroyFunc ToggleFocusPolicy
AddToFunc ToggleFocusPolicy
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy sloppy_focus) \
	ChangeFocusPolicy ClickToFocus
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy sloppy_focus) \
	Exec $FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 1 \
	ClickToFocus SloppyFocus click_focus sloppy_focus
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy sloppy_focus) \
	Exec xmessage -center "Focus policy is now ClickToFocus." -title Info
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy sloppy_focus) \
	InfoStoreAdd focus_policy click_focus
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy click_focus) \
	ChangeFocusPolicy MouseFocus
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy click_focus) \
	Exec xmessage -center "Focus policy is now MouseFocus." -title Info
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy click_focus) \
	Exec $FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 1 MouseFocus ClickToFocus \
	mouse_focus click_focus
+ I Test (EnvMatch infostore.focus_policy click_focus) \
	InfoStoreAdd focus_policy mouse_focus
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I ChangeFocusPolicy SloppyFocus
+ I Exec xmessage -center "Focus policy is now SloppyFocus." -title Info
+ I Exec $FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 1 SloppyFocus MouseFocus \
	sloppy_focus mouse_focus
+ I InfoStoreAdd focus_policy sloppy_focus

DestroyFunc ChangeFocusPolicy
AddToFunc ChangeFocusPolicy
+ I Style * $0
# Setting Style * <focus_policy> isn't enough as that will override
# all conflicting styles. Thus we reset all focus related styles here.
+ I Style * FPLenient, FPSortWindowlistByFocus, FPGrabFocus
# Application specific settings
+ I Style "FvwmPager" NeverFocus
+ I Style "FvwmButtons" NeverFocus

DestroyFunc ChangeTheme
AddToFunc ChangeTheme
+ I Exec $FVWM_USERDIR/scripts/update-configs.sh 3 $0
+ I Restart

### Tiling functions
DestroyFunc TileLeft
AddToFunc TileLeft
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 100
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move +0 +0

DestroyFunc TileRight
AddToFunc TileRight
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 100
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move -0 +0

DestroyFunc TileTop
AddToFunc TileTop
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 100 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move +0 +0

DestroyFunc TileBottom
AddToFunc TileBottom
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 100 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move +0 -0

DestroyFunc TileTopLeft
AddToFunc TileTopLeft
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move +0 +0

DestroyFunc TileTopRight
AddToFunc TileTopRight
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move -0 +0

DestroyFunc TileBottomLeft
AddToFunc TileBottomLeft
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move +0 -0

DestroyFunc TileBottomRight
AddToFunc TileBottomRight
+ I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Maximize 50 50
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized, !Shaded, !Iconic) Move -0 -0

